    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A race to stay ahead of a coming flood, Teddy's Volcanic Voyage is a precision platformer emphasizing control and real time decision making. Choose your path as you run, jump, and soar your way through this dark underground world.  Collect volcanic salmon and magical artifacts to power your journey. Featuring randomized world generation and hand drawn pixel art, this retro style game will keep you on your toes as you strive to reach new heights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cover Art by Alejandro C @thekickestudio</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Art by Gerezek @germanio</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music by KVNE</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sound Design by Mihu @hzsmith</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
